,Not Recommended,227480,23290551,"Posted: 30 May, 2016",all,NioZero,"Nice shooter videogame. In this game you must face hordes of enemies in various different stages. Each horde are accompanied with special modifiers called ""Tests of Faith"" which add an interesting element and bring nice strategic touch. You can get coins and experience to level up your character which allow different types of customization like appearance and weapons. You can also upgrade the weapons for more damage, ammo, etc.But I cannot recommend this game for various reasonsThe game is short. Only five stages. Although the tests of faith allow for more random encounters, after a while the game becomes repetitive.The game is completely abandoned. If you want to play alone it will be almost impossible to find a match. The only way is to play with friends. The game support up to four players online. One side-note; you cannot join a match after it started so if a friend want to play, you must start from the beginning of the stage.The game crashes constantly, specially at the beginning of a match. The crashes are almost random and after i tried multiple solution on Internet, the game still unplayable in most cases. Added to that, the developer stopped giving updates after more than three years."
